{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-474-last-digits-of-divisors","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 474: Zadnji brojevi delitelja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za pozitivan ceo broj $n$ i poslednje cifre $d$, definišemo $F(n, d)$ kao broj delitelja $n$-a čije zadnje cifre su jednake $d$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $F(84, 4) = 3$. Među delilateljima 84 (1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 12, 14, 21, 28, 42, 84), tri od njih (4, 14, 84) imaju broj koji se završava na 4.</p>\n<p>Možemo takođe da potvrdimo da $F(12!, 12) = 11$ na $F(50!, 123) = 17\\,888$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $F({10}^6!, 65\\,432) \\text{ modulo } ({10}^{16} + 61)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5471000cf542c510059","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302151,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-474-last-digits-of-divisors"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function lastDigitsOfDivisors() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nlastDigitsOfDivisors();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>lastDigitsOfDivisors()</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>9690646731515010</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(lastDigitsOfDivisors(), 9690646731515010);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-474-last-digits-of-divisors","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"